        <section id="strengthen-basic-arithmetic">
            <h2>1. Strengthen Basic Arithmetic and Algebra</h2>
            <p>Algebra is the foundation of almost every advanced math topic.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Topics to Cover:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Solving linear equations</li>
                        <li>Understanding polynomials and factoring</li>
                        <li>Simplifying expressions</li>
                        <li>Working with exponents and roots</li>
                        <li>Inequalities and absolute values</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Resources:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Book:</strong> <em>Algebra for Dummies</em> by Mary Jane Sterling</li>
                        <li><strong>Free Course:</strong> <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/math/algebra-basics" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Khan Academy - Algebra Basics</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
        <section id="geometry-and-trigonometry">
            <h2>2. Dive Deeper into Geometry and Trigonometry</h2>
            <p>Gain a solid understanding of shapes, angles, and trigonometric functions.</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Topics to Cover:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li>Properties of triangles, circles, and polygons</li>
                        <li>Sine, cosine, tangent, and trigonometric identities</li>
                        <li>Graphs of trigonometric functions</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
                <li><strong>Resources:</strong>
                    <ul>
                        <li><strong>Book:</strong> <em>Geometry for Enjoyment and Challenge</em> by Richard Rhoad</li>
                        <li><strong>Free Course:</strong> <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/math/geometry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Khan Academy - Geometry</a> and <a href="https://www.khanacademy.org/math/trigonometry" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Trigonometry</a></li>
                    </ul>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </section>
